<div data-controller="appear">
  <h1 class="type-serif-heading text-center animate-fade-in-up" style="font-size: var(--text-3xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Things to Do</h1>
  <p class="text-center animate-fade-in-up delay-1" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-12); max-width: 40rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
    The surrounding area is full of wonderful experiences. Below are a few we'd recommend during your stay.
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="card appear">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Historic Village</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          A short drive from the venue, this hilltop village is one of the most striking in the area. Arrive early to wander the quiet stone lanes, take in the panoramic views, and stop into the small boutiques and cafes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Market Town</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          A town that captures the charm of the region — morning markets, shaded squares, bakeries, galleries and little streets lined with beautiful buildings.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Scenic Drive</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          For those wishing to explore further, the surrounding countryside is one of the most rewarding regions to drive through. Each village has its own character: hilltop views, vineyard surrounds and quiet cafes. It's an easy loop and makes for a memorable day trip.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Nearby City</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          A completely different side of the region — historic architecture, contemporary galleries, and excellent restaurants. The old town is especially lovely in the late afternoon.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card appear">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Local Dining</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          The region is known for its exceptional food, whether you're after a long, indulgent lunch or something simple and classic. There's no shortage of places that showcase the best local cuisine. We recommend booking ahead.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
